reviewText: The writers' of Diagnosis Murder are extremely talented!  Dick Van Dike seems to never change, just a Great Actor!  The support cast are very good as well!  I especially like Amanda Blake and Jessie (the young blonde doctor)
summary: THESE ARE GREAT TO WATCH OVER & OVER AGAIN!!
